  "detailed_description": "Mythic Dungeons is a simple 2.5D Platformer Game.<br><br>Inspired by Castlevania HD, this title has arcade-like gameplay with high replayability and easy playability.<br><br>It also supports online cooperative play, with up to 10 players.<br><br>The multiplayer matching system uses a drop-in - drop-out system, making it easy and convenient to join a multiplayer game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mythical dungeon awaits</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291970/extras/79452005c47f0e57527d52b03620497d.avif?t=1660389757\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br>There is only one rule: Defeat the tough boss at the deepest part of the dungeon within the time limit!<br><br>The dungeon is full of monsters and traps.<br><br>Survive the dungeon and bring back the treasure!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Four unique classes</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291970/extras/39eba3fd4431a8d3ae10d0dcd821b5c2.avif?t=1660389757\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br>Players can choose from four unique classes.<br><br>Each class has ample enhancements, including the ability to obtain new equipment, increase skill levels, and upgrade and enchant equipment.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Four unique classes</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Six distinctive levels and six bosses</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 800 equipment and items</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>37 magic and skills.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 100 avatar items</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online multiplayer for up to 10 players</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Mythic Dungeons is a simple 2.5D Platformer Game.<br><br>Inspired by Castlevania HD, this title has arcade-like gameplay with high replayability and easy playability.<br><br>It also supports online cooperative play, with up to 10 players.<br><br>The multiplayer matching system uses a drop-in - drop-out system, making it easy and convenient to join a multiplayer game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mythical dungeon awaits</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291970/extras/79452005c47f0e57527d52b03620497d.avif?t=1660389757\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br>There is only one rule: Defeat the tough boss at the deepest part of the dungeon within the time limit!<br><br>The dungeon is full of monsters and traps.<br><br>Survive the dungeon and bring back the treasure!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Four unique classes</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291970/extras/39eba3fd4431a8d3ae10d0dcd821b5c2.avif?t=1660389757\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br>Players can choose from four unique classes.<br><br>Each class has ample enhancements, including the ability to obtain new equipment, increase skill levels, and upgrade and enchant equipment.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Four unique classes</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Six distinctive levels and six bosses</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 800 equipment and items</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>37 magic and skills.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 100 avatar items</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online multiplayer for up to 10 players</li></ul>",
